  "body": "### Description\nWhen validating gossip messages, we need to consider whether execution payloads have been validated enough to gossip.  For blocks the parent block must be fully validated before gossiping on (but not the block itself).  Unsure on the requirement for attestations, the referenced head block likely needs to be fully validated.",
